	<module type="driver" id="sam0.drivers.nvm" caption="NVM - Non-Volatile Memory">
		<info type="description" value="summary">
			Driver for the SAM D20/D21/R21 Non-Volatile Memory controller. Provides a
			unified interface for the erasing, reading and writing of data to
			and from the various non-volatile memories of the device, including
			executable FLASH memory and user configuration pages.
		</info>

